OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FStrip searches of children by police
OL,8,Fare down by more than half in four
OL,9,Fyears but the Children's Commissioner
OL,10,Fhas questioned the use of force in
OL,11,Fsome cases and warned that ethnic
OL,12,Fdisparities persist.
OL,14,FThe issue came to prominence after a
OL,15,Fblack teenager was searched at school
OL,16,Fby officers while on her period in
OL,17,FDecember 2020.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
