CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FKnown as Child Q, she was 15 years old
OL,8,Fwhen the incident took place in
OL,9,FHackney, east London, after being
OL,10,Fwrongly suspected of carrying cannabis.
OL,12,FLast summer a disciplinary panel found
OL,13,Ftwo officers had committed gross
OL,14,Fmisconduct during the
OL,15,F"disproportionate" and "humiliating"
OL,16,Fincident, and the pair were dismissed
OL,17,Ffrom the Metropolitan Police without
OL,18,Fnotice.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@RO]wD@XOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/17
