OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FA report this week by Children's
OL,8,FCommissioner Dame Rachel de Souza's
OL,9,Foffice found no searches were recorded
OL,10,Fas happening at a school, in the
OL,11,Flatest period of July 2023 to June
OL,12,F2024, although it added that more than
OL,13,Fa quarter (26%) of search locations
OL,14,Fwere not recorded.
OL,16,FUsing data from the first half of
OL,17,F2024, her office estimated a total of
OL,18,F377 strip searches took place in the
OL,19,Fwhole of that year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FThis was down 56% on 854 searches in
OL,8,F2020.
OL,10,FWhile standard stop and searches can
OL,11,Finvolve removal of coats and jackets,
OL,12,Fstrip searching can involve exposure
OL,13,Fof intimate body parts and are
OL,14,Fgoverned by strict rules which
OL,15,Fofficers must follow including where
OL,16,Fthey take place and who should be
OL,17,Fpresent.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FDame Rachel said while there had been
OL,8,F"promising signs of progress in the
OL,9,Freduction of overall numbers, as well
OL,10,Fas how searches are carried out and
OL,11,Frecorded, this progress is masking the
OL,12,Ffact that too many are still
OL,13,Funnecessary, unsafe and underreported".
OL,15,FShe said "too many children" are still
OL,16,Fbeing "let down by systemic failures
OL,17,Fand treated as adults while they are
OL,18,Fstill children".
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@fO]wD@JOUwD@\O]xD@GOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/17
