OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FHer report, published on Wednesday,
OL,8,Ffound some searches between July 2023
OL,9,Fand June 2024 were still being carried
OL,10,Fout in public view (26) and with no
OL,11,Fappropriate adult present (22).
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FThe data also showed that three in 10
OL,8,F(30%) strip searches in that time
OL,9,Fperiod involved children who had
OL,10,Falready been searched at least once
OL,11,Fbefore, which the commissioner warned
OL,12,Frisked "significant and repeated
OL,13,Fdamage to their mental wellbeing,
OL,14,Ftheir relationship with the police,
OL,15,Fand showing a clear failure to
OL,16,Fsuccessfully intervene with children".
OL,26,@tD@HOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
