OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FForce, such as handcuffs or firearms
OL,8,Fand Tasers, was used in almost a fifth
OL,9,F(17%) of all stop and searches of
OL,10,Fchildren between April 2024 and March
OL,11,F2025, her report added.
OL,13,FBut in 43% of instances where force
OL,14,Fwas used, no further action was taken,
OL,15,Fwhich the commissioner said called
OL,16,Finto "question the use of necessary
OL,17,Fand proportionate tests".
OL,26,@xD@FOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FWhile the vast majority of stop and
OL,8,Fsearches of children in that period
OL,9,Fwere on those aged 11 to 17 ( 22,437),
OL,10,Fthere were 46 instances of use of
OL,11,Fforce in a stop and search of children
OL,12,Faged under 11.
OL,14,FThe commissioner also warned of
OL,15,Fcontinued ethnic disparities, saying
OL,16,Fblack children were almost five times
OL,17,Fas likely to have force used during a
OL,18,Fsearch than white children.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FIn cases where force was used against
OL,8,Fa white child to be searched, officers
OL,9,Fwere more likely to note them as
OL,10,Fhaving a mental health need, but for
OL,11,Fblack children the reason identified
OL,12,Fwas more often their size or build,
OL,13,Fher report said.
OL,15,FDame Rachel said: "We cannot accept
OL,16,Fthat black children are subjected to
OL,17,Fuse of force because of the way they
OL,18,Fare perceived."
OL,26,@wD@SOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FShe described strip searching as "an
OL,8,Fintrusive and traumatic experience"
OL,9,Fand said it should "only ever be used
OL,10,Fas a last resort when there is an
OL,11,Fimmediate risk of serious harm".
OL,13,FShe added: "A much higher threshold
OL,14,Fshould be met before a child is
OL,15,Fsubjected to a humiliating and
OL,16,Ftraumatising strip search.
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@cO]qD@TOUsD@_O]uD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,F"Moving forward, it is vital that
OL,8,Fprogress continues, with fewer
OL,9,Fsearches carried out, better data
OL,10,Frecording when they do, and for the
OL,11,Fimproving practice seen in some forces
OL,12,Fto be emulated across the country `
OL,13,Fonly then will we build a culture of
OL,14,Ftrust between children and the police."
OL,16,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,17,F(NPCC) said updates, which were out
OL,18,Ffor public consultation, to official
OL,19,Fguidance on stop and search would
OL,20,Fensure a "child-centred approach" was
OL,21,Ftaken by officers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@gO]|D@JOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FDeputy Chief Constable Andy Mariner,
OL,8,Fwho is NPCC lead for stop and search,
OL,9,Fsaid the changed guidance "strengthens
OL,10,Fsafeguarding requirements, and places
OL,11,Fgreater emphasis on the quality of the
OL,12,Fencounter ` including communication,
OL,13,Fde-escalation, and dignity", and "sets
OL,14,Fclear expectations on the use of force
OL,15,Fand the use of handcuffs and is
OL,16,Fsimpler and more practical".
OL,26,@qD@[OUuD@[O]uD@bOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FHe said: "While there are positive
OL,8,Fsigns in that the number of strip
OL,9,Fsearches have been falling over time,
OL,10,Fwe continue to work with policing
OL,11,Fpartners, stakeholders and academics
OL,12,Fto understand and address the
OL,13,Fdisproportionate use of stop and
OL,14,Fsearch, which we understand can
OL,15,Fundermine trust between policing and
OL,16,Fcommunities."
OL,26,@oD@JOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/17
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FHe said that while the use of stop and
OL,8,Fsearch, including strip search, was a
OL,9,F"legitimate and useful policing tool
OL,10,Fto help us in removing dangerous
OL,11,Fweapons and drugs from the streets",
OL,12,Fforces also acknowledged that "when it
OL,13,Fis used inappropriately, it can damage
OL,14,Four relationships with affected
OL,15,Fcommunities".
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@cO]tD@_OUwD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/17
