PN,40716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776942175
OL,3,CChild strip searches fall but
OL,4,Ccommissioner raises questions over use
OL,5,Cof force
OL,7,FA Home Office spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We're introducing extensive
OL,9,Fsafeguards for children and young
OL,10,Fpeople for strip searching and
OL,11,Fbringing in reforms to drive up
OL,12,Fstandards in policing, improve vetting
OL,13,Fand tackle misconduct."
